comments: Fox (SAC) moves slightly forward towards Markkanen (CLE)  and marginal contact occurs during his drive to the basket.
Fox (SAC) reaches across Markkanen's(CLE) front and makes contact to his arm that affects his pass attempt.
Hield (SAC) is moving alongside Mobley's (CLE) path and he absorbs the marginal contact during the drive.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Markkanen (CLE) places his arm to Haliburton's (SAC) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Markkanen (CLE) is moving alongside Haliburton's (SAC) path and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Queta (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Markkanen's (CLE) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Allen (CLE) slides his arm against Haliburton's (SAC) shoulder and marginal contact occurs after Haliburton has released his shot attempt.
Markkanen (CLE) jumps towards Haliburton (SAC) and marginal contact occurs with Haliburton's slightly extended forearm after the release of his shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) applies a stayed hand to Garland's (CLE) side and marginal contact occurs after Garland has released his shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) clamps Allen's (CLE) arm as they pursue the loose ball and the contact affects Allen's ability to retrieve the rebound.
Allen (CLE) and Hield (SAC) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Haliburton (SAC) extends his arm into Mobley's (CLE) side prior to making any contact with the ball.
Barnes (SAC) places his hand momentarily on Mobley's hip before immediately removing his hand.
Queta (SAC) makes contact with Allen's (CLE) arm and the contact causes Allen to lose control of the ball.
Haliburton (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mobley (CLE) during rebounding.
Queta (SAC) and Allen (CLE) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Garland (CLE) makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mobley (CLE).
Barnes (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mobley (CLE) as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Rondo (CLE) brushes Fox's (SAC) left arm and immediately removes his hand as Fox is gathering the ball.  The contact occurs prior to Fox's upward shooting motion.
